aspsms-t Road MAP

Version 1.2
-----------

* Stable release basic features

* Check if aspsms.notification.pl and webserver is prober configured an 
  write a syslog message.

* Better exeptionhandling for sms notifications

* Interface to query balance for user

Version 1.3
-----------

* WAPPush support

* Automatic change to cheaper method (sms/mms)

* UNICODE support

Not scheduled
-------------

* Full Two-Way support for everyone. A separate two-way number is not longer necessary

* Bug: If a USERKEY is two times registred to the transport, sms notifications will be
       sent to the first found entry.
